$OpenBSD$

+-----------------------------------------------------------------------
| Running ${FULLPKGNAME} on OpenBSD
+-----------------------------------------------------------------------

To run yquake2 on OpenBSD, you need the original Quake II (point release) files.

Copy ctf/*.pak to ${TRUEPREFIX}/share/yquake2/ctf/
and start up yquake2.

quake2 +set game ctf
